* John Thomas Abdy (1854)
* Edwin Charles Clark (1873)
* William Warwick Buckland (1914)
* Patrick William Duff (1945)
* Peter Gonville Stein (1968)
* David Eric Lothian Johnston (1993)
* David John Ibbetson (2000)
* Helen Scott (2022)
