The sequence abuts because formula_190 holds for all formula_191 if formula_192 and formula_193. To see this, note that either the domain or the codomain of the differential is zero for the considered cases. In visual terms, the sheets stabilize in a growing rectangle (see picture above). The spectral sequence need not degenerate, however, because the differential maps might not all be zero at once. Similarly, the spectral sequence also converges if formula_35 vanishes for all formula_122 greater than some formula_185 and for all formula_186 greater than some formula_187.

